Jdd,

I would get the 3.44 ratio. I put a 3.88 in my 64 big nut bus. Wish I had 
put in the 3.44 with my 1776 engine.

Also, while the tranee is out, replace the torsion arm bushings!!. I just 
replace the outer bushings and the bus wanders significantly less as I 
cruise down the freeway.

Chris 
